                            <comment id="13723982" author="yukim" created="Tue, 30 Jul 2013 15:52:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like this is a regression from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5555&quot; title=&quot;Allow sstableloader to handle a larger number of files&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5555&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5555&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
(I think workaround is to use sstableloader from 1.2.6).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached unit test for SSTableLoader. if run with &apos;ant test-compression -Dtest.name=SSTableLoaderTest&apos;, it fails as described above.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13724218" author="thobbs" created="Tue, 30 Jul 2013 18:21:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch 0002 creates a common Interface for the two Compressed*File classes to allow access to the compression metadata without casting.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
